467\" height=\"192\" src=\"/Public/Uploads/image/201507/8typhzh.jpg\" title=\"利用分光光度法测定送检单位提供的4份苜草素样品中总皂苷的含量。\" align=\"\" alt=\"利用分光光度法测定送检单位提供的4份苜草素样品中总皂苷的含量。\" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">2. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;\">检测目标</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:24.0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">利用分光光度法测定送检单位提供的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">份苜草素样品中总皂苷的含量。</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">3. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;\">检测方法</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">3.1 </span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">检测波长的确定</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">4.</span><span style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:16px;line-height:normal;font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:黑体;\">检测结果</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:24.0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">送检单位提供的</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">份苜草素样品总皂苷的含量在</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">36.29-41.44 mg/g</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">之间，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">号样品含量最高，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">1-3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">号样品的总皂苷含量接近，</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">份样品间差异均不显著（表</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">，</span><i><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">P</span></i><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">&gt;0.05</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">）。</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">份苜草素样品总皂苷的含量均低于杨江涛等</span><sup><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">[1]</span></sup><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">的报道（总皂苷含量</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;\">≥5%</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">）。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">5. </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">主要结论</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\"></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:24.0pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\