ine-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">吴莹莹</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">苜草素多糖、黄酮和皂苷对小鼠巨噬细胞</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\">RAW264. 7B -</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">防御素基因表达的影响</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\">. </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">畜牧兽医学报</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;line-height:150%;\">, 2010, 41( 5) : 608 – 614.</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:right;text-indent:210pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">检测操作人：</span><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">焦晓林</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:right;text-indent:210pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">检测负责人：</span><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">高微微</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:right;text-indent:210pt;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">报告日期：</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp; <u>2014</u></span><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">年</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;\">7</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:宋体;\">月</span></u><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-heig